creator: Naturally Slim
descriptionHtml:
Download the Naturally Slim app to access your Naturally Slim program anytime, anywhere. Learn the psychology-based, lifelong skills for weight loss that sticks, less stress, better sleep, and more—no restrictive diets, calorie-counting, or specialty foods required. With the Naturally Slim program, you’ll learn to change when and how you eat, not what you eat, so you can improve your physical and mental health without giving up the foods you love. Get started or continue your journey now with the app.

By downloading the app, you get:

• Access to your complete library of personalized lessons from our team of experts
• Unique and clinically-proven behavior-change skills to improve your whole health
• Psychology-based tools for building mindful eating skills that form lifelong habits
• The ability to set goals and monitor your weight & physical activity progress
• Our 10-5-10 meal timer to make it easier to slow down and savor your food
• Feedback and support to help you when you need it
• Prompts and reminders to keep you motivated to reach your health improvement goals
• Integration with fitness trackers or devices

If you are already enrolled in the Naturally Slim program, just download the app and log in. If you would like to enroll, visit www.naturallyslim.com to learn how you can learn lifelong skills to better your health in just ten weeks.

creator: Naturally Slim
descriptionHtml:
Download the Naturally Slim app to access your Naturally Slim program anytime, anywhere. Learn the psychology-based, lifelong skills for weight loss that sticks, less stress, better sleep, and more—no restrictive diets, calorie-counting, or specialty foods required. With the Naturally Slim program, you’ll learn to change when and how you eat, not what you eat, so you can improve your physical and mental health without giving up the foods you love. Get started or continue your journey now with the app.

By downloading the app, you get:

• Access to your complete library of personalized lessons from our team of experts
• Unique and clinically-proven behavior-change skills to improve your whole health
• Psychology-based tools for building mindful eating skills that form lifelong habits
• The ability to set goals and monitor your weight & physical activity progress
• Our 10-5-10 meal timer to make it easier to slow down and savor your food
• Feedback and support to help you when you need it
• Prompts and reminders to keep you motivated to reach your health improvement goals
• Integration with fitness trackers or devices

If you are already enrolled in the Naturally Slim program, just download the app and log in. If you would like to enroll, visit www.naturallyslim.com to learn how you can learn lifelong skills to better your health in just ten weeks.

Bring mindfulness to mealtime with our 10-5-10 timer

Learn practical, scientifically-proven skills from experts

Receive personal guidance and support from our coaches

Practice what you eat with our meal log

Progress makes perfect - track yours

Set goals - we’ll celebrate victories together

Download the Wondr app to access your Wondr Health program anytime, anywhere. Wondr takes what we’ve been told to believe about health and weight loss... and flips it upside down. Forget the points, plans and restrictions. Our skills-based digital weight loss program will teach you the science of how to eat the foods you love so you can lose weight, feel better and live stronger. Get started or continue your journey now with the app.

By downloading the app, you get:

Access to your complete library of personalized lessons from our team of experts

Daily and weekly tasks, plus a personal progress dashboard and goal setting, to keep you on track

Our 10-5-10 meal timer to make it easier to slow down and savor your food

Feedback and support to help you when you need it

Prompts and reminders to keep you motivated to reach your health improvement goals

Integration with fitness trackers and HealthKit so that you can easily track weight and steps

If you are already enrolled in the Wondr Health program, just download the app and log in. If you would like to enroll, visit www.wondrhealth.com to learn how you can learn lifelong skills to better your health in just ten weeks.

descriptionShort: Wondr is a skills-based behavioral change program, focused on weight management.
title: Wondr Health

creator: Naturally Slim
descriptionHtml:
Wondr is a digital weight loss program tailored to you. Wondr goes beyond diet fads to teach you science-based skills that will help you lose weight without giving up the foods you love. Forget the points, plans, and restrictions. You’ll learn simple, behavioral skills from experts that will help you not only lose weight but feel better, increase your energy level, improve your sleep, and simply live a stronger, healthier life.

By downloading the app, you get:

* Weekly video lessons with clinically-proven skills for results that last

* Access to a diverse library of lessons from our team of experts tailored to you

* Personalized support and reminders through daily texts and nudges

* Progress dashboard and goal setting, to keep you on track

* Our 10-5-10 meal timer makes it easier to slow down and savor your food

* Cooking videos and delicious recipes from the Wondr kitchen

* Movement recommendations to help you ease pain and feel your best

* Activity videos to inspire more physical activity

* Integration with fitness trackers and HealthKit so that you can easily track weight and steps.

* Personal guidance and support from our health coaches to help reach your goals

* The WondrLink™ online community for support from other Wondrers (past & present)
